    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "那是我作为圣骑士的\\n第一个任务——\\n镇压彼茨教区的内乱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "因为赴任彼茨教区的主教被杀害，\\n各种暴动陡然激增，演变成了\\n一场教会与民众之间的内乱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "最终，背叛教会的许多民众\\n以伊莉雅之名被判处有罪。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "女神伊莉雅啊，愿您洗清他们\\n灵魂中的污秽，引导他们的魔力。\\n愿女神赐予慈悲……安息吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "圣骑士",
            "context": "德莱茨，你那边埋葬好了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "嗯，这是最后一个了。\\n我能问……一个问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "圣骑士",
            "context": "什么问题？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "我们的肃清\\n有必要做得如此绝情吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "圣骑士",
            "context": "都是他们自作自受……\\n这是那些忘记伊莉雅的庇佑、\\n自甘堕落的人应得的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "圣骑士",
            "context": "因此，为了不让他们的灵魂变得更污浊，\\n我们的使命就是用女神之刃救赎他们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "圣骑士",
            "context": "好了，要是都埋葬完了，\\n就收拾一下瓦砾吧。我先走了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "救赎……吗……\\n嗯！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "刚才的石子是？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "儿童",
            "context": "你这个……杀人犯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "快住手！求、求你了！\\n请放过这个孩子！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "儿童",
            "context": "妈妈，为什么！？\\n这个人，明明是杀死爸爸的凶手！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "冷静一点。\\n我没有攻击你们的意思。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "战争已经结束了。\\n我没有理由对你们拔刀相向。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "那么……那么，\\n你为什么杀了我丈夫！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "因为……他杀死了主教大人，\\n还袭击了教会……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "儿童",
            "context": "骗子！明明是你们教会\\n先把大家带走的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "把大家带走？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "是啊……说什么\\n“这是献给龙的活祭”！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "献给龙的活祭？\\n什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "可别说你不知道……\\n这都是，教会主教说过的话啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "一开始说什么为了献祭给龙、\\n为了教会的发展，\\n逼迫我们大量捐款……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "后来变本加厉，声称只有被召唤到\\n龙身边才能得到真正的救赎，\\n强行向我们索要活祭！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "什么！\\n那种荒唐的教诲……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "既然你们是教会的人，就告诉我们啊！\\n我们只是想得到幸福，\\n为什么我们非死不可啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "伊莉雅教的教诲，已经疯了！\\n那是教唆杀人的教诲啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "圣骑士",
            "context": "喂！刚才的话我可不能听过算数！\\n快把异端给我抓起来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "请等一下！\\n这个人的话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "圣骑士",
            "context": "话就留在异端审问的时候说吧。\\n过来！还有那边那个小孩！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "啊……刚才的话，不是的！\\n住手！不要啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "这就是……这样的就是……\\n所谓的救赎吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "伊莉雅教徒信奉女神伊莉雅，\\n献上自己的祈祷……\\n为了得到幸福而不断地努力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "但他们努力到最后，\\n却是这种悲惨的下场吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "既然如此，\\n伊莉雅教究竟是为何而……\\n伊莉雅啊……请您指引我前行……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "也就是说，彼茨内乱\\n是因为教会的失控？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "没错。而且，整个内乱都是\\n由于扭曲的信仰而导致的恶果。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "如果信仰堕落为\\n残害无辜生命的工具，\\n那它就是应该舍弃的遗物。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "难道，你倒戈向炼狱文书\\n就是因为……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "嗯，我认为只要\\n为教会带来新的变化，\\n或许就能拯救更多生命。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "就算变革需要牺牲，\\n只要将来能够实现安稳的世界，\\n那么这种牺牲也是必要的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "但是，即便如此也远远不够。\\n教会依然在不断腐败与恶化，\\n因此，就需要采取进一步的措施。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "所以，你就对龙拔刀相向了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "为什么一定要伤害龙？\\n没有其它办法了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝，正确的信仰\\n和异端的教诲密不可分。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "我不会强求你的理解。\\n只是，你别再插手这件事了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你觉得……这样就好吗？\\n再这样下去，你免不了火刑。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你的志向还没有实现，\\n甘心就这样被烧死吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "正义唯有天知。\\n倘若我是异端之志，理应被裁决。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "我不会为了保全自己，\\n而轻易放弃自己的信仰。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "德莱茨……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "已经够了吧。\\n好了，快回去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "（我已经明白德莱茨为什么会对\\n长久以来的教会抱有疑问了，但是……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "（他内心挂念的，依旧是人们的幸福——\\n自始至终都没有变过……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "女神伊莉雅啊，请您告诉我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "所谓信仰……所谓异端……\\n到底是什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "距离异端审判\\n还有两天",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}